************************<br>
<br>
Few other spells that were added to this list, but my top pick is Blessing of Reverence, 10% spellcasting haste buff. It compliments many of our new spells extremely well. I wish it lasted longer and/or had a group version available, but it was a wonderful surprise and highly useful.<br>
<br>
We also got a new undead DoT, which is still pretty rarely needed, although it's not bad if you find a situation of use.<br>
<br>
Can't wait for Yaulp6. Will be very useful... the extra mana regen while standing will be a god-send since I'm almost NEVER sitting and medding now, except between fights.... heal aggro is just much too bad.<br>
<br>
Pacification (a Lull-type spell) will also be pretty useful for xp groups, since they've now actually FIXED the line of spells. Don't have yet though =P<br>
<br>
In conclusion... PoP totally changed the game for me as a high-end raiding cleric. It's intense, it's viscious and I'm having more fun this past month than probably ever before in this game. =)  <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:xx-small;"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=47567">Morinkhan</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> | <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.furys-edge.com">Fury's Edge</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Morell Thule</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ulaani>ulaani</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Qeynos Newbie</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#628CBC>(11/27/02 3:46:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Spell list for PoP?</span><hr size=1> I have to agree. PoP has added the fun factor back into the game. I love supernal remedy. Its amazing what a difference casting speed makes. And the graveyard feature is really great too. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-size:xx-small;"><br>
